src/pods/file/api-multi-file.decorator.ts

ApiFile
Default value : (fileName = 'file'): MethodDecorator => (target: any, propertyKey: string, descriptor: PropertyDescriptor) => { ApiBody({ schema: { type: 'object', properties: { [fileName]: { type: 'string', format: 'binary', }, }, }, })(target, propertyKey, descriptor); }

src/utils/group-by-properties.ts

arrayFromObject
Default value : <T>(obj: T): T[Extract<keyof T, string>][] => { const arr = []; for (const i in obj) { arr.push(obj[i]); } return arr; }
groupByProps
Default value : <T, U, K>( array: T[], callback: (listItem: T) => U[], ): K[] => { const groups: any = {}; array.forEach((item): void => { const group: string = JSON.stringify(callback(item)); groups[group] = groups[group] || []; groups[group].push(item); }); return arrayFromObject(groups); }

src/utils/array.ts

asyncReduce
Default value : async <T, U>( array: T[], callback: (previousValue: U, currentValue: T) => Promise<U>, initialValue: U, ): Promise<U> => { let result = initialValue; for (const item of array) { result = await callback(result, item); } return result; }

baseReadServiceProvider
Type : object
Default value : { provide: BASE_READ_SERVICE, useFactory: (configService: ConfigService) => { if (configService.get<string>('MODE') == 'CI') { return new BaseReadServiceForCi(); } else { return new BaseReadService(configService); } }, inject: [ConfigService], }

src/utils/bigNumber.ts

bigNumAvg
Default value : (values: BigNumber[]): BigNumber => values.length > 0 ? bigNumSum(values).div(BigNumber.from(values.length)) : BigNumber.from(0)
bigNumMin
Default value : (...values: BigNumber[]): BigNumber => values.reduce((min, value) => { return value.lt(min) ? value : min; }, values[0])
bigNumPercentage
Default value : (part: BigNumber, total: BigNumber): number => { if (total.eq(0)) { return 0; } return part.mul(1000).div(total).toNumber() / 10; }
bigNumSum
Default value : (values: BigNumber[]): BigNumber => values.reduce((sum, value) => sum.add(value), BigNumber.from(0))

ormconfig-dev.ts

config
Type : ConnectionOptions
Default value : { ...getDBConnectionOptions(), entities: ['src/**/*.entity.ts'], synchronize: false, migrationsRun: true, migrations: ['migrations/*.ts'], migrationsTableName: 'migrations_drec', cli: { migrationsDir: 'migrations', }, }
getDBConnectionOptions
Default value : (): ConnectionOptions => { return process.env.DATABASE_URL ? { type: 'postgres', url: process.env.DATABASE_URL, ssl: { rejectUnauthorized: false, }, } : { type: 'postgres', host: process.env.DB_HOST ?? 'localhost', port: Number(process.env.DB_PORT) ?? 5432, username: process.env.DB_USERNAME ?? 'postgres', password: process.env.DB_PASSWORD ?? 'postgres', database: process.env.DB_DATABASE ?? 'origin', }; }

src/utils/get-capacity-range.ts

getCapacityRange
Default value : (capacityInKiloWatts:number): CapacityRange =>{ let capacityWatts = capacityInKiloWatts * (10 ** 3); let capacityMegaWatts = capacityInKiloWatts * (10 ** -3); if (capacityWatts <= 1000) { return CapacityRange.firstRange; } else if (capacityInKiloWatts > 1.01 && Math.round(capacityInKiloWatts) <= 50) { return CapacityRange.secondRange; } else if (capacityInKiloWatts >= 51 && Math.round(capacityInKiloWatts) <= 500) { return CapacityRange.thirdRange; } else if (Math.round(capacityInKiloWatts) > 500 && Math.round(capacityMegaWatts) <= 5) { return CapacityRange.fourthRange; } else if (Math.round(capacityMegaWatts) > 5) { return CapacityRange.fifthRange; } }

src/utils/get-commissioning-date-range.ts

getDateRangeFromYear
Default value : ( commissioningDate: string, ): CommissioningDateRange => { const year = new Date(commissioningDate).getFullYear(); const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear(); const range = currentYear - year; if (range === 0) { const month = new Date(commissioningDate).getMonth(); if (month < 4) { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_1_Q1; } else if (month >= 4 && month < 7) { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_1_Q2; } else if (month >= 7 && month < 10) { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_1_Q3; } else { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_1_Q4; } } else if (range === 1) { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_2; } else if (range === 2) { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_3; } else if (range === 3) { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_4; } else if (range === 4) { return CommissioningDateRange.Year_5; } else if (range >= 6 && range <= 10) { return CommissioningDateRange.Between_years_6_10; } else if (range >= 11 && range <= 15) { return CommissioningDateRange.Between_years_11_15; } else { return CommissioningDateRange.Above_15_years; } }

src/utils/checkForISOStringFormat.ts

isValidUTCDateFormat
Default value : (dateInput:string) =>{ let dateFormateToCheck = new RegExp(/\d\d\d\d\-\d\d\-\d\dT\d\d:\d\d:\d\d\.\d{1,}Z/); ; const dateFormat = 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ'; const momentDateFormatToCheck = moment(dateInput).format(dateFormat); return dateFormateToCheck.test(dateInput) && moment(momentDateFormatToCheck, dateFormat, true).isValid(); }
